{"type": "article", "id": 26607, "title": "玻璃器皿", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134945V1yfUMNqrnpQIhuG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://campanas.com.br/en\">Campana 兄弟</a>去年曾为 LASVIT 设计过一款色彩斑澜的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/campana-brothers-lasvit-06-24-2015/\">枝形吊灯</a>，这一次他们将类似的概念用在了这一套同样名为 Candy 的玻璃器皿上。手吹玻璃中的色带看上去像是把焦糖放在器皿的顶端，沿着轮廓滑下所造成的痕迹。Campana 兄弟在挑选颜色时只是将浅色系和深色系搭配在一起，并不遵守其他特定的原则，每一个器皿也因此独一无二。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134943i49AGbB3qTOsIV8L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03422983\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134943ZYRbSsrj28a76tQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09046455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134944iVXURLgWaeITOb8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134944QgI6Sl8mtXp50FC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}